caption.text:
Submission for adidas x parley contest.  Parley AIR (Avoid + Intercept + Redesign)
It has been our responsibilities as human being to preserve our nature, especially oceans. It is due to the fact that oceans are the largest ecosystems on earth, they are the earth's largest life support systems.
Indonesia was named the second-largest contributor of plastic waste in the ocean. According to goverment data, people consume up to 9.8 billion plastic bags every year in indonesia. And as indonesian people that data shocked me. So why don't we reduce plastic consumption? Every house in indonesia should have old newspaper, why don't we replace plastic bag with "news"paper bag which is indeed sutainable? This is a video of how i process old newspaper into a paper bag, that can replace plastic bag. #parleyAIR #adidasxparley  #adidasindonesia #adidascontest @adidasindonesia @parley.tv @adidas size: #us9
